Open it.

496
00:28:38,070 --> 00:28:39,196
[Morgan exhales]

497
00:28:40,156 --> 00:28:42,199
Yeah.

498
00:28:42,283 --> 00:28:44,744
I heard you had to jump through hoops

499
00:28:44,827 --> 00:28:47,496
to get that thing back to me,
and I thought…

500
00:28:48,831 --> 00:28:52,418
"What a perfect engagement gift."
Am I right?

501
00:28:53,294 --> 00:28:54,295
[necklace clinks]

502
00:28:54,378 --> 00:28:55,671
Yeah.

503
00:28:56,714 --> 00:28:57,840
