504
00:28:57,923 --> 00:28:59,759
Welcome to the family.

505
00:29:02,428 --> 00:29:04,388
[funky music playing]

506
00:29:05,890 --> 00:29:07,057
I'll take that.

507
00:29:12,146 --> 00:29:13,105
[man exhales]

508
00:29:13,189 --> 00:29:14,398
Salute.

509
00:29:18,235 --> 00:29:19,236
Oh, right there.

510
00:29:19,320 --> 00:29:21,071
[music continues]

511
00:29:23,866 --> 00:29:24,867
Too tight?

512
00:29:25,451 --> 00:29:26,994
-Yeah, a little bit.
-Oh…

513
00:29:27,661 --> 00:29:29,330
You'll get used to it.

514
00:29:30,831 --> 00:29:31,832
There.

515
00:29:32,708 --> 00:29:34,710
I thought you worked in real estate.

516
00:29:34,794 --> 00:29:36,128
Mm, I do.

517
00:29:36,212 --> 00:29:38,339
Among other things, obviously.

518
00:29:39,882 --> 00:29:42,092
Mm. Aw.

519
00:29:42,176 --> 00:29:43,219
Look at that.

520
00:29:43,302 --> 00:29:44,261
[music ends]

521
00:29:44,345 --> 00:29:46,305
Oh. Keep it safe.

522
00:29:46,388 --> 00:29:49,308
Don't want it ending up in another grave.

523
00:29:49,391 --> 00:29:50,392
Okay.

524
00:29:50,476 --> 00:29:53,020
And if you run over my son again,

525
00:29:53,103 --> 00:29:55,731
then I will fucking kill you myself.

526
00:29:57,858 --> 00:29:58,859
Shall we?

527
00:30:00,152 --> 00:30:01,445
