528
00:30:01,529 --> 00:30:02,988
Big smiles, everyone.

529
00:30:03,489 --> 00:30:05,533
-[guests laughing]
-[retro music playing]

530
00:30:12,164 --> 00:30:13,999
-Morgan.
-I need to talk to you.

531
00:30:14,083 --> 00:30:15,417
The Italians are here.

532
00:30:15,501 --> 00:30:18,921
Um, that makes a lot of sense,
because Annette is their boss.

533
00:30:20,005 --> 00:30:21,340
What are you talking about?

534
00:30:21,423 --> 00:30:25,469
Ivan and Andrei work for the Italians.
The Italians work for Annette.

535
00:30:26,095 --> 00:30:27,513
It was for her.

536
00:30:28,138 --> 00:30:30,349
It has all been for her.

537
00:30:31,976 --> 00:30:33,060
[glass clinking]

538
00:30:33,143 --> 00:30:34,228
Everybody!

539
00:30:34,311 --> 00:30:35,229
[glass clinking]

540
00:30:36,021 --> 00:30:39,441
Our mayor, Linda Morelli!

541
00:30:39,525 --> 00:30:40,651
[people applauding]

542
00:30:40,734 --> 00:30:43,904
Everybody, thank you. It's amazing
where life can take you.

543
00:30:43,988 --> 00:30:44,822
[people laughing]

544
00:30:44,905 --> 00:30:49,243
Now, I know that only half
of the people in the town voted for me,

545
00:30:49,326 --> 00:30:54,790
but trust me when I say that I will work
to make this whole town proud.

546
00:30:54,874 --> 00:30:56,500
[all cheering, applauding]

547
00:30:56,584 --> 00:31:00,671
Um, I want to thank my daughter, Natalie,

548
00:31:00,754 --> 00:31:03,716
who's been by my side
throughout everything,

549
00:31:03,799 --> 00:31:07,720
and Nicky and Morgan
for doing all that you do,

550
00:31:07,803 --> 00:31:13,100
and a very special thank-you
to Annette Zofrea

551
00:31:13,183 --> 00:31:15,436
for making tonight's event possible.

552
00:31:15,519 --> 00:31:18,272
Annette, you are a lifesaver.

553
00:31:18,355 --> 00:31:20,566
She is my good luck charm,

554
00:31:20,649 --> 00:31:27,197
and I cannot wait for our families
to come together officially very soon.

555
00:31:27,281 --> 00:31:28,198
[laughs]

556
00:31:28,282 --> 00:31:29,450
[people applauding]

557
00:31:29,533 --> 00:31:31,535
[big band music playing]

558
00:31:34,830 --> 00:31:36,123
[glasses clinking]

559
00:31:36,206 --> 00:31:38,542
I think we're in hell.
I… I think this is hell.

560
00:31:38,626 --> 00:31:39,752
[Morgan exhales heavily]

561
00:31:39,835 --> 00:31:40,794
-Hey, babe.
-Hey.

562
00:31:43,005 --> 00:31:45,424
-[Natalie laughing]
-[Linda laughing loudly]

563
00:31:46,342 --> 00:31:48,886
Um, I need, uh, two triple vodka sodas.
What do you want?

564
00:31:48,969 --> 00:31:51,472
I don't want anything.
Morgan, what are we gonna do?

565
00:31:51,555 --> 00:31:52,848
I forgot to vote.

566
00:31:53,390 --> 00:31:56,310
Too much on my plate. Forgot to vote.

567
00:31:56,393 --> 00:31:59,313
My mommy almost lost because of me.

568
00:31:59,396 --> 00:32:01,774
Okay, well, she didn't, okay?
So everything's fine.

569
00:32:01,857 --> 00:32:03,734
Just go party with Kev. Whatever.

570
00:32:03,817 --> 00:32:05,110
Kev.

571
