-Morgan.
-Mm-hmm.

572
00:32:06,236 --> 00:32:07,947
Natalie, can we have five minutes?

573
00:32:08,030 --> 00:32:09,281
Stop it, stop!

574
00:32:09,365 --> 00:32:11,241
-You guys are always interrupting me.
-Oh my God.

575
00:32:11,325 --> 00:32:13,786
Stop it. I am talking to my sister.

576
00:32:14,286 --> 00:32:17,915
Morgan, do not fucking do it.

577
00:32:17,998 --> 00:32:18,916
Do what?

578
00:32:18,999 --> 00:32:22,252
Marry Max, Morgan, don't.

579
00:32:22,336 --> 00:32:23,921
-Excuse me?
-Oh my God.

580
00:32:24,004 --> 00:32:27,091
Kevin is so fucking boring,
he makes me want to die.

581
00:32:27,174 --> 00:32:29,385
Natalie, I think you've had
a lot to drink, okay?

582
00:32:29,468 --> 00:32:34,348
Die, die, die. Like, I go home
every night, and he is just there,

583
00:32:34,431 --> 00:32:38,811
like, sitting at his computer
with his erectile dysfunction

584
00:32:38,894 --> 00:32:41,230
and his familial enmeshment issues and…

585
00:32:41,313 --> 00:32:43,565
-Jesus Christ, Natalie.
-I know, I know.

586
00:32:43,649 --> 00:32:45,234
But there comes a point, Morgan,

587
00:32:45,317 --> 00:32:48,070
when being in a situation
that you do not like

588
00:32:48,153 --> 00:32:50,447
starts to hurt.

589
00:32:50,531 --> 00:32:51,782
If I were you,

590
00:32:52,282 --> 00:32:55,077
I would get the fuck out
while you still can.

591
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:56,328
Excuse me.

592
00:33:01,959 --> 00:33:04,336
Not to be overly sentimental,

593
00:33:04,420 --> 00:33:08,674
