601
00:33:21,979 --> 00:33:23,689
I never cared much

602
00:33:23,772 --> 00:33:25,190
Oh! Look at me now…

603
00:33:25,274 --> 00:33:27,151
Bring it in a little tighter.

604
00:33:27,234 --> 00:33:28,235
All right.

605
00:33:28,736 --> 00:33:29,945
To family.

606
00:33:30,446 --> 00:33:31,947
To family.

607
00:33:32,031 --> 00:33:33,449
[people applauding]

608
00:33:36,952 --> 00:33:39,413
Three, two, one.

609
00:33:39,496 --> 00:33:42,166
Oh! Look at me now

610
00:33:42,249 --> 00:33:45,377
["Oh! Look At Me Now" (Live at Manhattan
Center) by Frank Sinatra playing]

611
00:33:45,461 --> 00:33:49,089
I'm a new man better than

612
00:33:49,173 --> 00:33:51,717
Casanova at his best

613
00:33:51,800 --> 00:33:52,718
Ta-da

614
00:33:52,801 --> 00:33:54,011
[laughter]

615
00:33:54,094 --> 00:33:55,846
Ta-da-da-da-di-da-dum

616
00:33:55,929 --> 00:33:57,097
I forgot it.

617
00:33:57,181 --> 00:33:59,516
I'm so proud I'm busting my vest

618
00:33:59,600 --> 00:34:01,602
I'm a lover

619
00:34:01,685 --> 00:34:05,189
So I'm the guy who bought a big jewel

620
00:34:05,272 --> 00:34:09,193
Yes, I'm the guy
Who finally fell in love and such

621
00:34:09,276 --> 00:34:11,737
I never cared much

622
00:34:11,820 --> 00:34:14,239
But look at me now

623
00:34:15,741 --> 00:34:19,536
Oh! Look at me now

624
